Revision history for Log-Dispatch-UnixSyslog

0.004     2025-07-10 11:55:54-04:00 America/New_York
        - now that we openlog just in time when logging, do not openlog eagerly
          at construction

0.003     2025-07-10 10:54:40-04:00 America/New_York
        - re-openlog after fork, mostly to compensate for IO::Async::Process's
          weird "close all fds" behavior on fork (even without exec)

0.002     2022-12-31 20:56:06-05:00 America/New_York
        - update author contact info
        - add perl version expectations to docs

0.001     2020-08-12 11:46:57-04:00 America/New_York
        - first version, released on an unsuspecting world
